To start the program, please run these commands from the root folder:
  - npm run instal
  - npm run dev

To populate the databse, feel free to add or delete users from the handleUsers page

please enter these lines as well as a secret token (jwt) in a .env file
to ensure correct functiunality:
  DB_LOGIN=neo4j
  DB_PWD=2j54A%

Note for 42 computers to install neo4j please follow these steps:
  - Managed Software Center, install JDK8
  - Check for updates in the MSC and install them
  - brew install neo4j
  - neo4j start --> you can now access the server from browser on localhost:7474
  - connect to the browser and connect to with
    - username: neo4j